  <p>You've probably heard a lot about ChatGPT. But lately, a new name keeps coming up everywhere — <strong>Claude AI</strong>. Tech journalists are calling it one of the smartest AI assistants available today. But if you're a complete beginner, you're probably wondering: what even is Claude AI, and should I be using it?</p>

  <p>That's exactly what this guide answers. We'll explain Claude AI in plain, simple language — no jargon, no hype — and show you exactly what it can do for you as a student, professional, or curious person in 2026. By the end, you'll know what Claude is, how it works, and how to start using it today for free.</p>

  <div class="callout callout-purple">
    <div class="callout-icon-row">
      <div class="callout-icon-wrap">💡</div>
