  <h2 id="what-can-it-do">What Can Claude AI Do? 6 Real Uses for Beginners</h2>

  <p>Here are six practical ways beginners are using Claude AI right now — with real examples you can try immediately.</p>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card-item">
      <div class="card-icon ci-purple">✍️</div>
      <h4>Writing Assistant</h4>
      <p>Draft emails, essays, blog posts, cover letters, and social captions. Tell Claude your topic and tone — it writes a solid first draft you can edit and personalise.</p>
